 * group:links => 链接设置
 * links.column1_title => 栏目1标题:text:Product
 * links.column1_items => 栏目1链接:textarea:Features=>#features\r\nPricing=>#pricing\r\nIntegrations=>/integrations\r\nChangelog=>/changelog|格式：名称=>链接，一行一个
 * links.column2_title => 栏目2标题:text:Company
 * links.column2_items => 栏目2链接:textarea:About=>/about\r\nBlog=>/blog\r\nCareers=>/careers\r\nContact=>/contact|格式：名称=>链接，一行一个
 * links.column3_title => 栏目3标题:text:Legal
 * links.column3_items => 栏目3链接:textarea:Privacy=>/privacy\r\nTerms=>/terms\r\nCookies=>/cookies|格式：名称=>链接，一行一个
 * group:copyright => 版权设置
